By Gabriel Ewepu- AbujaFederal Government has promised to boost agricultural research institutionswith patent rights on seeds multiplication to improve and increase food production. This was made known by the Minister of Agriculture and Rural Development, Mohmmed Nanono, at the 2019 Farmers Field Day and Seed Fair, held in Sheda, Abuja, which was organised by the National Agricultural Seed Council, NASC, in collaboration with Seed Entrepreneurs Association of Nigeria, SEEDAN. Continue reading 2019 Farmers Field Day: FG to boost research institution at Vanguard News. Source: Vanguard